    "en": {
      "title": "The Sri Lankan cricket team is looking for the Asian cricket crown",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Twenty20 cricket team led by Dasun Shanaka, who will participate in the Asia Cup cricket tournament starting on the 27th of this month in the United Arab Emirates, left for Dubai this afternoon (24).",
        "Before leaving for the tournament, captain Dasun Shanaka said that although any international tournament is a challenge, the Sri Lankan team participating in this tournament is a strong team.",
        "Dasun further said that this Sri Lankan team, which consists of many senior and young players, has more confidence in batting, but even though several senior bowlers are injured, they also have a strong bowling line-up.",
        "The Sri Lankan team is scheduled to play against Afghanistan in the first match of the preliminary round on 27th of this month."
      ],
